<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Women's Salon & Spa</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ff6699;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .salon-option {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 250px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            background-color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: block;
        }

        .salon-option:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .salon-option img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .salon-option h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .salon-option p {
            color: #666;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #ff6699;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Back navigation arrow */
        .back-arrow {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Women's Salon & Spa</h1>
    </header>

    <section>
        <form method="post" action="/salonw1">
        <button  class="salon-option" id="salon-wm">
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-19 at 5.07.19 PM.png" alt="Salon for Women">
            <h2>Salon for Women</h2>
            <p>Indulge in a world of beauty with our specialized salon services for women. Enjoy waxing, classic manicures , pedicures
                <br> and more.</p>
        </button>
        </form>
        <form method="post" action="/spaw1">
        <button class="salon-option" id="spaw">
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-19 at 5.07.26 PM.png" alt="Spa for Women">
            <h2>Spa for Women</h2>
            <p>Relax and rejuvenate with our luxurious spa treatments designed exclusively for women. Pamper yourself with massages, facials, and more.</p>
        </button>
        </form>
        <form method="post" action="/hairw1">
        <button class="salon-option" id="hairw" >
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-19 at 5.07.35 PM.png" alt="Hair Studio for Women" >
            <h2>Hair Studio for Women</h2>
            <p>Transform your hair with our professional hair styling services. From trendy cuts to elegant updos, we cater to your unique style.</p>
        </button>
        </form>
        <form method="post" action="/nailw1">
        <button class="salon-option" id="nailw">
            <img src="Screenshot 2023-11-19 at 5.07.41 PM.png" alt="Nail Studio for Women">
            <h2>Nail Studio for Women</h2>
            <p>Pamper your hands and feet with our nail studio services. Choose from a variety of nail art designs and  manicures and pedicures.</p>
        </button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Women's Salon & Spa. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <a href="salonhome.html" class="back-arrow">&#8592; Back</a>

</body>

</html>